OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUS food firm fined after   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchildren worked nights     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A major food sanitation company in the 
OL,6, US has agreed to pay $1.5m (#1.25m),   
OL,7, after investigators found it had       
OL,8, employed dozens of children to clean   
OL,9, meatpacking plants on overnight shifts.
OL,11,FMore than 100 teenagers, ages 13-17,   
OL,12,Fworked for Packers Sanitation Services,
OL,13,Fthe Department of Labor said.          
OL,15,FThe agency called it a "systemic"      
OL,16,Ffailure by the company.                
OL,18,FNational laws bar employment of        
OL,19,Fchildren under the age of 14 and limit 
OL,20,Fthe hours teenagers can work.          
